com.concordia.SOEN6461.util.calandar

Class CalendarCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.concordia.SOEN6461.util.calandar.CalendarCache

  • public class CalendarCache
extends java.lang.Object
    Cache all the calendar item information to keep from re-thrashing on every panel pass. Also save the list of components used to display this item, so they can be managed.
